text: Man, this game made me often wonder just what the hell my SNES was capable of! Awesome soundtracks, blazing graphics (for its day of course) but the thing that tripped me out the most was the final battle song. It starts out sounding like one of those rides at a grocery store you stick a quarter in and all of a sudden it turns into this SUPER AGRESSIVE metal jam. I was like geez, what in the HELL?LMAO!
